    v2 = (((v1 + 0.12 - v1 + 0.56) - (v0 + 0.11 + v2 + 0.87)) + 0.10)
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.27)) + ((v2 + 0.07 / v0 + 0.01) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.30)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.10 * v0 + 0.40)) + wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.40)))
